__d53s7 link-module__move-left__CCZH6 collapsible-caption-module__symbol__943UJ"" fill=""#666"" width=""0"" height=""0""><path fill=""#666"" d=""M15 6c.6 0 1 .4 1 1s-.4 1-1 1H9c-.6 0-1 .4-1 1v14a1.1 1.1 0 0 0 .2.6c.1.2.4.4.8.4h14c.6 0 1-.4 1-1v-6c0-.6.4-1 1-1s1 .4 1 1v6a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H9a3 3 0 0 1-2.2-.9A3 3 0 0 1 6 23V9a3 3 0 0 1 3-3Zm10 0 .4.1.5.5.1.4v6c0 .6-.4 1-1 1s-1-.4-1-1V9.4l-5.3 5.3a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3 1 1 0 0 1-.7-.3 1 1 0 0 1 0-1.4L22.6 8H19c-.6 0-1-.4-1-1s.4-1 1-1Z""></path></svg><span style=""border: 0px; clip: rect(0px, 0px, 0px, 0px); clip-path: inset(50%); height: 1px; margin: -1px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: absolute; width: 1px; white-space: nowrap;"">, opens new tab</span></span></a></span></div></figure></div><div class=""article-body-module__content__bnXL1""><div data-testid=""ContextWidget"" class=""context-widget-module__container__b9mKr article-body-module__context_widget__sq1EI""><div data-testid=""TabContainer"" class=""context-widget-module__tabcontainer__O1B-s""><ul role=""tablist"" class=""context-widget-module__tabs__AIjL0""><li data-testid=""summary-tab"" role=""tab"" aria-selected=""true"" tabindex=""0"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__medium__2Rl30 text-module__small__sph8i body-module__base__o--Cl body-module__small_body__gOmDf context-widget-module__tab__lRw-D context-widget-module__selected__Et295"">Summary</li><li data-testid=""companies-tab"" role=""tab"" aria-selected=""false"" tabindex=""-1"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__medium-grey__yZtlg text-module__medium__2Rl30 text-module__small__sph8i body-module__base__o--Cl body-module__small_body__gOmDf context-widget-module__tab__lRw-D"">Companies</li></ul></div><div data-testid=""ContextWidgetContent"" class=""context-widget-module__content__lI1uo""><ul data-testid=""Summary"" class=""summary-module__summary__QjADA""><li data-testid=""Body"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__base__o--Cl body-module__small_body__gOmDf summary-module__point__UgXPz"">Gold hits record high of $4,116.77/oz, silver at $52.12/oz</li><li data-testid=""Body"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__base__o--Cl body-module__small_body__gOmDf summary-module__point__UgXPz"">BofA lifts 2026 gold forecast to $5,000/oz, sees silver at $65</li></ul></div></div><div data-testid=""paragraph-0"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__full_width__kCIGb body-module__small_body__gOmDf article-body-module__paragraph__Ts-yF"">Oct 13 (Reuters) - Gold broke through $4,100 per ounce for the first time on Monday, hitting another record high on renewed U.S.-China trade tensions and expectations of U.S. interest rate cuts, while silver also rose to an all-time high.</div><div data-testid=""paragraph-1"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__full_width__kCIGb body-module__small_body__gOmDf article-body-module__paragraph__Ts-yF"">Spot gold was up 2.2% to $4,106.48 per ounce, as of 01:47 p.m. ET (1747 GMT), after hitting a record $4,116.77.</div><p data-testid=""promo-box"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__base__o--Cl body-module__small_body__gOmDf article-body-module__promo-box__hVl8h"">The Reuters Iran Briefing newsletter keeps you informed with the latest developments and analysis of the Iran war. Sign up  <a data-testid=""Link"" referrerpolicy=""no-referrer-when-downgrade"" href=""/newsletters/reuters-iran-briefing/?location=article-paragraph&amp;redirectUrl=%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fgold-hits-record-high-us-china-trade-woes-escalate-silver-scales-all-time-peak-2025-10-13%2F"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__inherit-color__PhuPF text-module__inherit-font__1P1hv text-module__inherit-size__EyiQW link-module__link__INqxZ link-module__underline_default__-okuC"">here.</a></p><div data-testid=""paragraph-2"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__full_width__kCIGb body-module__small_body__gOmDf article-body-module__paragraph__Ts-yF"">U.S. gold futures for December settled 3.3% higher at $4,133.</div><div data-testid=""paragraph-3"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__small__sph8i body-module__full_width__kCIGb body-module__small_body__gOmDf article-body-module__paragraph__Ts-yF"">Gold has climbed 56% this year and scaled the $4,000 milestone for the first time last week, driven by factors including geopolitical and economic uncertainties, expectations of U.S. interest rate cuts and robust central bank buying.</div><div data-testid=""element"" class=""article-body-module__element__5eCce""><div data-testid=""ResponsiveAdSlot"" class=""divider-container-module__container__MpXC- default divider-container-module__max-width__KpWSo""><div class=""ad-slot-module__container__VEdre ad-slot-module__fixed-height__W8iWX"" style=""--height: 455px;""><span data-testid=""Label"" class=""text-module__text__0GDob text-module__dark-grey__UFC18 text-module__regular__qJJtA text-module__extra_small__8Buss label-module__label__Sv2H2 label-module__small__0kHqa ad-slot-module__scroll-notice__VBF3B"">Advertisement Â· Scroll to continue</span><div class=""ad-slot-module__inner__tEY-D ad-slot-module__native__-BIBT""><div><div class=""ad-slot-module__slot__rdFsT"" id=""reuters_desktop_native_1"" name=""reuters_desktop_native_1"" style="""" data-integralas-id-bfc9b574-a0f2-a31e-cfd0-c287b5a0f13e="""" data-integralas-id-f2f9420c-bace-1ecf-1b76-2ebad8fd356f="""" data-integralas-id-f7add4a9-4551-69f